OL,7,FScotland's drug death rate has
OL,8,Fdecreased to its the lowest level
OL,9,Fsince 2017, but it still remains
OL,10,Fhigher than the rest of Europe.
OL,12,FIn 2022, there was a decrease of 279
OL,13,Fdeaths between 2021 and 2022 in
OL,14,FScotland, according to new data from
OL,15,FNational Records of Scotland (NRS).
OL,17,FSome 1,051 drug misuse deaths were
OL,18,Fregistered in Scotland in 2022 - a
OL,19,F21% decrease compared to 2021 - the
OL,20,Flargest year-on-year decrease on
OL,21,Frecord.
OL,3,CScotland drug deaths rate decreases -
OL,4,Cbut remains higher than the rest of
